divs: Sighting Details2nd event was a day later out facing Baltimore,the naked eye looked like a flicker star looked thru scope and saw the same.. A few days ago saw it out my back window again at 3 am got the scope and it was round shacking on a hale pivital motion with a crack of light near the bottom. as i watched it had three black oval like shapes one at 12 and the other at4 and8. they moved across the cicle to the crack of light, all then forming one black area. Then it was shaking and looked as if something was shadowing it and was not round and formed into what looked like a skull or allien shape with a small black circle at the left side above the middle...Very Creapy...No one can tell me what it is...Have you had any other sittings like this?
